  abstract={This article introduces the application of the improved K-means clustering algorithm in vocational Chinese education. Vocational Chinese language education is an important link in cultivating professional abilities and comprehensive qualities, and effective teaching methods and personalized teaching strategies play an important role in improving students' Chinese language proficiency. The application of integrated machine learning algorithms can help teachers better understand the learning characteristics and needs of students, thus conducting targeted teaching.Firstly, this article introduces the significance and goals of vocational Chinese language education. The Chinese language education in vocational colleges should not only cultivate students' language expression and communication skills, but also focus on cultivating students' professional literacy and comprehensive thinking abilities. Therefore, personalized teaching and precise learning evaluation are important directions for vocational Chinese education.Secondly, this article explores the application of the improved K-means clustering algorithm in vocational Chinese education. The traditional K-means clustering algorithm only considers the distance and similarity between samples, but in vocational Chinese education, it also needs to consider factors such as students' learning characteristics and background. Therefore, this article proposes an improved K-means algorithm that incorporates students' learning characteristics and needs as additional information into the clustering process, thereby achieving more accurate student grouping and personalized teaching.Then, this article introduces the practical application of the improved K-means algorithm in vocational Chinese education. By collecting and analyzing students' learning data and personal information, a student model is established, and an improved K-means algorithm is used to divide students into different groups. Teachers can develop corresponding teaching plans and personalized teaching strategies based on the learning characteristics and needs of different groups, to improve teaching effectiveness and student satisfaction.Finally, this article summarizes the application value of the improved K-means clustering algorithm in vocational Chinese education. By applying the improved K-means algorithm, teachers can better understand students' learning characteristics and needs, provide personalized teaching and learning support, and help improve students' language proficiency and comprehensive quality.},
