  pages={1-4},
  abstract={This paper based on the digital twin concept, relying on the Unity 3D platform, comprehensively uses the Internet of Things technology, Internet technology, cloud services and other means to link the physical physical scene of Prefabricated building construction training with the three-dimensional digital virtual scene in real time, virtual and real interaction, real-time synchronous intelligent perception, detection and feedback of the training process, and integrate teaching, training and evaluation. The system enable trainees to conduct theoretical learning and practical training in both virtual and real scenarios, efficiently completing teaching, training, and evaluation objectives.},
